[size=4]Description:[/size]

[/b][/color][size=3]Small player home near Dragon Bridge.[/size][size=3]

In order to get inside the house you need a key that is located inside a satchel that is inside a fallen tree (when facing the house form the road tree is located on your left side, check screenshots for exact location of satchel)

This house interior was designed to more or less resemble its exterior size and shape. It contains all crafting stations.
Inside you can find various custom containers along with some unnamed chests and other sorage.
All smithing related crafting stations you can find outside along with storage for smithing supplies, firewood and some unnamed barrels.


Whole thing is navmeshed and cleaned with TES5Edit.

[/size][size=3]


This file contains custom resources and new meshes created by myself, if you
want to use any of them be sure to give proper credit.[/size]
